---

<section class="where section section-cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="where__heading reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Where We're Going</p>
      <h2>The road ahead.</h2>
      <ul class="where__list">
        <li>Three sites in active development across California, Nevada, and Texas.</li>
        <li>Urban cluster development underway in Missouri.</li>
        <li>Big Sky Network development advancing across Montana.</li>
        <li>Detailed pipeline available to <a class="where__nda-link" href="/investors">qualified investors under NDA</a>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="where__cta reveal">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/investors">
        Request investor briefing
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
          <polyline points="13 6 19 12 13 18" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://fieldnotes.rangewayev.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Subscribe to Field Notes
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .where__heading {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-7);
  }

  .where__heading h2 {
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .where__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: var(--space-5) 0 0;
    max-width: 68ch;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .where__list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .where__list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-warm-deep);
  }

  .where__nda-link {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .where__nda-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-warm-deep);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .where__cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-7);
  }
</style>
